4164005|archive-date=2019-05-29|url-status=live}}</ref> Gameplay footage and screenshots exists.<ref name=\"ONMvb\"/><ref name=\"VBCES\"/>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"| '''''Star Seed'''''\n| {{N/A}}\n| Coconuts Japan Entertainment\n| Coconuts Japan Entertainment\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"| '''''Strange Animal School'''''\n| Life simulation\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{date|1995-09-17}}\n| Unknown if actual development started beyond announcement.<ref name=\"CSGvb\">{{cite book|last=|first=|title=CSG|publisher=Consumer Soft Group|date=17 September 1995|pages=1\u201320|language=ja}}</ref>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"| '''''[[Street Fighter II: The World Warrior|Street Fighter II]]'''''\n| Fighting\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{date|1995-07}}\n| Unknown if actual development started on Virtual Boy version beyond rumor.<ref>{{cite magazine|last=|first=|url=https://www.planetvb.com/modules/articles/?s020278003|title=Software - \u30d0\u30fc\u30c1\u30e3\u30eb\u30dc\u30fc\u30a4 \u300e\u30b9\u30c8\u30ea\u30fc\u30c8\u30d5\u30a1\u30a4\u30bf\u30fc\u2161\u300f!?|magazine=[[Famitsu]]|issue=336|publisher=[[ASCII Corporation|ASCII]]|date=May 26, 1995|page=91|lang=ja|access-date=September 29, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530092854/https://www.planetvb.com/modules/articles/?s020278003|archive-date=May 30, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|last=Des Barres|first=Nicholas|url=https://archive.org/stream/Gamefan_Vol_3_Issue_07#page/n91/mode/1up|title=Japan Now - News & Rumors|magazine=[[GameFan]]|volume=3|issue=7|publisher=DieHard Gamers Club|date=July 1995|page=90|access-date=2019-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181129120834/https://archive.org/stream/Gamefan_Vol_3_Issue_07#page/n91/mode/1up|archive-date=2018-11-29|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"| '''''Sunday's Point'''''\n| {{N/A}}\n| Coconuts Japan Entertainment\n| Coconuts Japan Entertainment \n| {{date|1998-01-31}}\n| 